text: Rush Creek may refer to: ==Communities== * Rush Creek, Queensland, Australia * Rush Creek Township, Fairfield County, Ohio, U.S. * Rush Creek, Wise County, Texas, U.S., a ghost town ==Waterways== * Rush Creek (New South Wales), a tributary of the Hawkesbury-Nepean catchment, in New South Wales, Australia * Rush Creek (Marin County, California) * Rush Creek (Mono County, California) * Rush Creek (Colorado) * Rush Creek (Kishwaukee River), a tributary of the Kishwaukee River in Illinois * Rush Creek (Root River), a stream in Minnesota * Rush Creek (Missouri River), a stream in Missouri
title: Rush Creek
